examples.en: I decided to tell her everything.
We're pretty happy with everything right now.

examples.en: People will buy everything she paints.

examples.en: Apart from the bus arriving late, everything else seemed to be going according to plan.
examples.ru: Если не считать опоздания автобуса, всё остальное вроде бы шло по плану.
